      <title>里德：就业报告“令人印象深刻”，美联储仍将采取行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-05/rieder-jobs-report-impressive-fed-will-still-move-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德全球固定收益首席信息官里克·里德(Rick Rieder)表示，3月份就业报告意味着美联储可能对利率政策更加耐心。他在彭博电视台接受了马努斯·克兰尼的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-05/rieder-jobs-report-impressive-fed-will-still-move-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:00:02 GMT</pubDate>
