      <title>乔·刘易斯宣判后加入亿万富翁重罪犯行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/joe-lewis-joins-ranks-of-billionaire-felons-after-sentencing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乔·刘易斯 (Joe Lewis) 因内幕交易被判处三年缓刑，加入了被定罪但仍设法保住财富的亿万富翁行列。]]></description>
