    <item>
      <title>井喷的就业数据增加了美联储推迟或减少降息的可能性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/blowout-jobs-report-raises-chance-of-delayed-fewer-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国近一年来最大的就业增长增加了美联储官员进一步推迟降息的可能性，并考虑今年的降息幅度少于预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/blowout-jobs-report-raises-chance-of-delayed-fewer-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:34:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管数据强劲，埃里安仍预计美联储今年将降息两次</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/el-erian-sees-two-fed-rate-cuts-this-year-despite-strong-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆罕默德·埃里安仍然预计美联储官员今年将降息两次，尽管一份重磅就业报告促使交易员重新考虑降息时机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/el-erian-sees-two-fed-rate-cuts-this-year-despite-strong-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 13:32:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
